sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant WebUI as Angular UI
    participant LangGraph as LangGraph Workflow
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL
    participant WorkflowAPI as Workflow API
    participant Agent as Specialist Agent

    Note over LangGraph: Workflow executing in IMPLEMENTING phase
    LangGraph->>Agent: Execute task
    Agent->>Agent: Detects protected action<br/>(push, PR, network, credentials)

    Agent->>LangGraph: Request approval<br/>(langgraph.types.interrupt)
    LangGraph->>LangGraph: Set status=WAITING_APPROVAL
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint with interrupt
    LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Create AgentApproval record<br/>(decision: pending)

    LangGraph->>WorkflowAPI: Publish event<br/>approval_requested
    WorkflowAPI->>WebUI: SSE event<br/>{type: approval_requested,<br/>approval_id, tool, description}

    WebUI->>User: Show approval dialog
    User->>WebUI: Review and decide

    alt User approves
        User->>WebUI: Click Approve
        WebUI->>WorkflowAPI: POST /runs/{run_id}/approvals/{id}/approve<br/>{decision: approved, decided_by}
        WorkflowAPI->>PostgreSQL: Update AgentApproval<br/>(decision: approved, decided_at)
        WorkflowAPI->>PostgreSQL: Update checkpoint<br/>(approval_decisions[last]=approved)
        WorkflowAPI->>LangGraph: Resume with Command<br/>(approval_decision: approved)
        LangGraph->>Agent: Execute protected action
        Agent-->>LangGraph: Action completed
        LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint<br/>(IMPLEMENTING)
    else User rejects
        User->>WebUI: Click Reject
        WebUI->>WorkflowAPI: POST /runs/{run_id}/approvals/{id}/reject<br/>{decision: rejected, decided_by}
        WorkflowAPI->>PostgreSQL: Update AgentApproval<br/>(decision: rejected, decided_at)
        WorkflowAPI->>PostgreSQL: Update checkpoint<br/>(approval_decisions[last]=rejected)
        WorkflowAPI->>LangGraph: Resume with Command<br/>(approval_decision: rejected)
        LangGraph->>LangGraph: Set status=FAILED
        LangGraph->>PostgreSQL: Save checkpoint (FAILED)
    end

    WorkflowAPI->>WebUI: SSE event<br/>{type: approval_decided,<br/>decision}
    WebUI->>User: Update UI with result
